OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FHeavy rain
OL,6,Fclearing to the east through the
OL,7,Fevening to leave the rest of the night
OL,8,Fdry with some clear spells developing.
OL,9,FStrong winds and risk of coastal gales
OL,10,Feasing.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FA dry morning with sunny
OL,13,Fspells. Becoming cloudier in the
OL,14,Fafternoon with outbreaks of rain which
OL,15,Fmay be heavy at times. Winds strong at
OL,16,Ftimes, especially near the coast.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
